		<img width="4096" height="2304" src="https://blog.redbus.pe/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/IMG_20170515_115945_814.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Valle de Jequetepeque" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://blog.redbus.pe/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/IMG_20170515_115945_814.jpg 4096w, https://blog.redbus.pe/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/IMG_20170515_115945_814-696x392.jpg 696w, https://blog.redbus.pe/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/IMG_20170515_115945_814-1068x601.jpg 1068w, https://blog.redbus.pe/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/IMG_20170515_115945_814-747x420.jpg 747w, https://blog.redbus.pe/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/IMG_20170515_115945_814-1920x1080.jpg 1920w, https://blog.redbus.pe/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/IMG_20170515_115945_814-300x169.jpg 300w, https://blog.redbus.pe/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/IMG_20170515_115945_814-768x432.jpg 768w, https://blog.redbus.pe/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/IMG_20170515_115945_814-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4096px) 100vw, 4096px" />		<div class="post-info-wrap">
